data.enText: a type of entertainment in which a machine plays only the music of popular songs so that people can sing the words themselves

data.chText: 卡拉OK机 / 之夜 / 酒吧

tr: singing popular songs accompanied by a recording of an orchestra (usually in bars or nightclubs)

value.def: Karaoke is a form of entertainment in which a machine plays the tunes of songs, and people take it in turns to sing the words.
